===方言保留问题===
{{see also|讲华语运动}}

自2000年代以来，新加坡华族社会之间越来越多人关切方言的保留。这是因为使用方言作为家庭用语的人数急跌。大多数少于40岁的新加坡华人有英语和华语的应用知识，却没有任何其他在新加坡使用的汉语言的知识。然而，绝大部分老一辈的新加坡华人只谙其他汉语言，只懂一点或不懂华语。因为这样，导致年轻一辈的国人与祖父母有语言上的沟通障碍。新加坡的华族文化和方言保护人士担心，方言的使用下降可导致最终新加坡不再使用方言<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.chineseoperainstitute.com.sg/pic/Translation%20in%20Chinese%20Opera.doc | format=doc | work=Chinese Opera Institute | location=Singapore | title=Translation and Chinese Opera: The Singapore Experience | first=Soon Pong | last=Chua | year=2007 | accessdate=2010-10-19 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110912003800/http://www.chineseoperainstitute.com.sg/pic/Translation%20in%20Chinese%20Opera.doc | archivedate=2011-09-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/413581/1/.html | work=ChannelNewsAsia | location=Singapore | title=Use of dialects interfere with learning of Mandarin & English | date=2009-03-06 | accessdate=2010-11-11 | archive-date=2009-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307112543/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/413581/1/.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Inter-generational cultural transmission in Singapore: A brief discussion | author = Liang, Chong Ching | year = 1999 | url = http://archive.ifla.org/IV/ifla65/65cc-e.htm | publisher = Oral History Centre, National Archives of Singapore | accessdate = 2014-02-01 | archive-date = 2016-01-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160124013317/http://archive.ifla.org/IV/ifla65/65cc-e.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

